des: Are you and your team practicing for an upcoming regional science bowl or the National Science Bowl? The Science Bowl skill, powered by ORAU, will allow you to practice for your competition just like a real event with Alexa serving as your moderator. All questions come from previous NSB competitions and are provided courtesy of the U.S. Department of Energy’s Office of Science.
